data.description: Open plan with LR, DR and kitchen in one great room with sun room and office/den adjacent. 2 large bedrooms and 2 baths. Large laundry room and big pantry off the kitchen. Extensive storage. Oversized 2 car garage with built in storage and work bench. Extensive upgrades. Slate floors. Granite in kitchen, baths and laundry room. Upgraded cabinetry in kitchen. Extensive landscaping with roses and day lilies. Very large back patio with gas hookup for grill.
data.whatILove: Active Seniors community. Superbly managed HOA. Outstanding financially. Home is just under 2,000 sq ft. Extensive landscape investment. 20+ roses of varying heights, colors and growing habits. A border with 80+ day lilies creating a sea of yellow in the summer. Both front and back patios. Front is east facing. Back is south and west. All counter tops (kitchen, laundry room and both bathrooms) are granite. Slate floors are wonderful. Kitchen cabinetry is upgraded. Large pantry.
